secondary_street_name: Prestwood Street, Tatlow Street, Stuart Street
description: Demolition of existing buildings and erection of a basement, part 3, 4 and 5 storey building at the Brewery Industrial Estate bounded by Prestwood Street, Taplow Street, Sturt Street and Wenlock Road, and a basement, part 7 and 8 storey building at 1-3 Wenlock Road. All to provide 104 residential units (35x1, 34x2, 25x3, 8x4 and 2x5 bed) including 36 affordable units and 1767 square metres of business floorspace (class B1a/b/c) and 143 sqm (class A1) / (class D1) /  (class B1a/b/c) floorspace, with associated cycle/car spaces
